<div type="head"><ab>Fürderbrief </ab></div>
<div type="content">
<ab>Als wir <add>Reicholf <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> und <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>Haidenab<ex>er</ex></expan></add>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> czu
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> gnedigen
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Osterreich
                            <expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan> von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> und
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> kauffleute notdurfft
                                <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, als <add>sie</add> ew wol erczelen
                        wirdt, also <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                            <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> ratgesellen in <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        und der <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> sachen
                            <expan>fürderlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, geraten und beholffen sein wöllet,
                        als etc. Das wöllen etc. <expan>Act<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Mathey
                                <expan>ap<ex>osto</ex>li</expan>.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Berhtold<ex>en</ex></expan>, bischof zu Freysing,
                                <lb/><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Burkh<ex>art</ex></expan> von Rabenstein,
                            <lb/><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hansen von Freuntstsperg, <lb/>der
                        stat czu Halle im Intal, <lb/>Bartholomes von Guvidaun, <lb/>her
                                <expan>Burkh<ex>art</ex></expan> von Mansperg, <lb/>graf
                                <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Metsch <expan>se<ex>ni</ex><hi rend="sup">ori</hi></expan>, <lb/>graf
                            <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>jung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> von Metsch, <lb/>graf
                                <expan>Wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan> von Metsch,
                            <lb/><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Wilhelm <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        Welden, <expan>ritt<ex>er</ex></expan>, <lb/><expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
                        Strewn, <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> zu Sterczing,
                                <lb/><expan>Nick<ex>las</ex></expan> Harrach,
                            <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> zu Inspruck. </ab>
</div>
